# Full Exception Map — All 3 Services

| Validation | Where Checked | Exception Thrown | HTTP Code |
|---|---|---|---|
| Mobile = 10 digits | `@Pattern` in DTO | `MethodArgumentNotValidException` | 400 |
| Email contains `@` | `@Pattern` in DTO | `MethodArgumentNotValidException` | 400 |
| Duplicate name | Service layer (DB check) | `DuplicateNameException` | 409 |
| ID not found | Service layer | `ResourceNotFoundException` | 404 |
| Duplicate email | Service layer | `UserAlreadyExistsException` | 409 |
| Wrong password | Service layer | `IllegalArgumentException` | 401 |
| Anything else | Fallback handler | `Exception` | 500 |

